tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE user_engagement_metrics (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    app_id UUID NOT NULL,
    engagement_date DATE NOT NULL,
    engagement_duration INT NOT NULL,
    engagement_action VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE marketing_strategies (
    strategy_id INT,
    strategy_name VARCHAR(50),
    platform VARCHAR(50),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE marketing_campaigns (
    campaign_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name VARCHAR,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    budget DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE user_engagement_metrics (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    device_id UUID,
    engagement_time TIMESTAMP,
    engagement_duration INTERVAL,
    engagement_event TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE ad_campaigns (
    campaign_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    campaign_budget DECIMAL,
    campaign_status TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE user_activities (
    activity_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    activity_type TEXT,
    activity_date DATE,
    activity_duration INTERVAL
)

CREATE TABLE app_installs (
    install_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    install_date TIMESTAMP,
    app_version TEXT,
    device_type TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE conversion_events (
    event_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    event_type TEXT,
    event_date TIMESTAMP,
    event_value DECIMAL
)
